---
layout: layouts/base
pagination:
  data: collections.tags
  size: 1
  alias: tag
permalink: /tags/{{ tag | slugify }}/index.html
computedTitle: "タグ - "
---

{%- set site = site | default({}) -%}

# 📌 タグ: {{ tag }}

{% set articlesWithTag = [] %}
{% for article in collections.articles %}
  {% if article.data.tags and article.data.tags.includes(tag) %}
    {% set articlesWithTag = articlesWithTag.concat(article) %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if articlesWithTag | length > 0 %}

## このタグの記事 ({{ articlesWithTag | length }})

{% for article in articlesWithTag %}
- **[{{ article.data.title }}]({{ article.url | url }})** — {{ article.data.publishedAt | dateISO }}
  {% if article.data.category %}
  _Category: {{ article.data.category }}_
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

---

## 他のタグを探す

[すべてのタグに戻る]({{ '/tags/' | url }})

{% else %}

このタグに記事はまだありません。

[ホームに戻る]({{ '/' | url }}){.btn}

{% endif %}
